title: How Will This Play Out?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and David Dennis Jr. debate how the process of the NFL seeking a one-year indefinite suspension for Deshaun Watson will play out from here, and what the chances are that ayahuasca helped Aaron Rodgers win back-to-back MVPs?
